@startuml svc-payments--post-payments

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #059669
    ParticipantBorderColor #374151
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
    LifeLineBorderColor #6B7280
    BoxBorderColor #94A3B8
    BoxBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
    NoteBorderColor #64748B
    NoteBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
}

header [[/microservices/svc-payments/#integration-context ⬆ svc-payments Integration Context]]

title POST /payments\nProcess a payment

participant "Client" as Client [[/applications/]]
participant "API Gateway" as GW [[/actors/#api-gateway]] #E0F2FE
participant "svc-payments" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-payments/]] #FEE2E2
participant "Currency Exchange API" as FX [[/actors/#currency-exchange-api]] #F3F4F6
participant "Fraud Detection API" as FD [[/actors/#fraud-detection-api]] #FEE2E2
participant "Payment Gateway" as PGW [[/actors/#payment-gateway]] #FEE2E2
participant "Notifications" as Ntfy [[/microservices/svc-notifications/]] #F1F5F9
database "PostgreSQL" as DB [[/microservices/svc-payments/#data-store]] #FEF9C3

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-payments.html#/Payments/processPayment View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : POST /payments
activate GW #059669
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #059669

note right of Svc : Validate request body

== Cross-Service Integration ==

Svc -> FX : Convert foreign currency to base currency
activate FX #F3F4F6
FX --> Svc : OK
deactivate FX

Svc -[#DC2626]> FD : Screen transaction
activate FD #F3F4F6
FD --[#DC2626]> Svc : OK
deactivate FD

Svc -[#DC2626]> PGW : Tokenize & route payment
activate PGW #F3F4F6
PGW --[#DC2626]> Svc : OK
deactivate PGW

== Database ==

Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO ...
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Created row
deactivate DB

== Async Events ==

Svc ->> Ntfy : [[/microservices/svc-notifications/#post-notifications-send-a-notification Send payment receipt]]

Svc --> GW : 201 Created
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 201 Created
deactivate GW

@enduml